---
title: Chicken, Zucchini & Tomato Flatbreads with Lemon Ricotta, Fresh Parsley, Honey & Chili Flakes
description: If this recipe could talk, it would say “I’m so fancy!” Toasty flatbreads are gussied up with fluffy lemony ricotta cheese, and bites of tomato and zucchini bursting with juicy goodness. Oh, and we have to talk about the bling (aka garnish) on top: parsley, chili flakes, and honey add savory-sweet contrast that makes each bite light up. You’ve just hit dinnertime gold.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/642af06e705ba288cf032418-efcabfd4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64ef6d3859668f196b417ca9.pdf
nutrition:
